highlights.text: “BON” by Number_i has been on Viral Songs Japan the longest, at 457 days straight.
PeanutsKun has the most spots on Viral Songs Japan. “Stop Motion (feat. Makaino Ririm)” is the highest at #4.
“GO!” by CORTIS is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Japan at #2.
“I Think I Like You Better When You’re Gone” by Reneé Rapp is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Japan, up 20 spots at #72.
